{"title":"线段树","uid":"a448dfd8ebb4408d1633f0dff8411f1c","slug":"线段树及拓展","date":"2026-01-24T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-01-24T17:59:09.684Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/线段树及拓展.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"线段树初步\"><a href=\"#线段树初步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"线段树初步\"></a>线段树初步</h1><h2 id=\"建树函数\"><a href=\"#建树函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建树函数\"></a>建树函数</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">const</span> <span class=\"type\">int</span> maxn = (<span class=\"type\">int</span>)<span class=\"number\">1e5</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">node</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, r, v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; a[maxn &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">2</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//因为线段树的高度是log_2 n,总占用需要最多4n，这里尽量往大了开。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> num[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">build</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    a[id].l = l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    a[id].r = r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l == r) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        a[id].v = num[l];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + r &gt;&gt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">build</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, l, mid);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">build</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, mid + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, r);<span class=\"comment\">//分别等价于 *2 与 *2+1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    a[id].v = a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v + a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"修改某些节点上的值\"><a href=\"#修改某些节点上的值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改某些节点上的值\"></a>修改某些节点上的值</h2><p>方案一：给某个节点赋值</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//赋值函数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">opt_1</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id, <span class=\"type\">int</span> k, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//id是从第id个节点出发，k是想要修改的点的位置（后面递归的部分实际上是二分），v是希望给这个点赋的值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> l = a[id].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> r = a[id].r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l == r) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        a[id].v = v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + r &gt;&gt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (mid &lt; k) <span class=\"built_in\">opt_1</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, k, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"built_in\">opt_1</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, k, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    a[id].v = a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v + a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">opt_2</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id, <span class=\"type\">int</span> tgtl, <span class=\"type\">int</span> tgtr)</span> </span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//调用这个函数，id一般得是根节点的下标（避免一开始节点的区间就被包裹）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//后面两个参数分别是区间的左右边界</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//返回值为一个从tgtl到tgtr的部分和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> l = a[id].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> r = a[id].r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (tgtl &lt;= l &amp;&amp; r &lt;= tgtr) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a[id].v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + r &gt;&gt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (mid &gt;= tgtr) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">opt_2</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, tgtl, tgtr);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (mid &lt; tgtl) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">opt_2</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, tgtl, tgtr);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">opt_2</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, tgtl, tgtr) + <span class=\"built_in\">opt_2</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, tgtl, tgtr);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//中间的if和else if是一个二分，即判断是往左走还是往右走</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//最关键的是最后一个return。通过这一行可以把零碎的子区间拼凑成需要的区间</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>方案二：给区间赋值</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//1，首先给每个节点增加一个成员</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">node</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> v;   <span class=\"comment\">// 区间和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> tag; <span class=\"comment\">// 标记：存储其每个下属节点需要加上的值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; a[maxn &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">2</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//2，分发函数：访问子节点前，把父节点的债（tag）分发给两个孩子。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">push_down</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 如果当前节点有标记（tag不为0）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (a[id].tag != <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> left = id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;      <span class=\"comment\">// 左孩子下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"type\">int</span> right = id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 右孩子下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> t = a[id].tag; <span class=\"comment\">// 取出标记值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 1. 更新左孩子的数值和标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 左孩子的新值 = 旧值 + 增加量 * 区间长度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[left].v += t * (a[left].r - a[left].l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[left].tag += t; <span class=\"comment\">// 累加标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 2. 更新右孩子的数值和标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[right].v += t * (a[right].r - a[right].l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[right].tag += t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 3. 清空当前节点的标记（债已还清）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[id].tag = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//3，修改区间值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// id:当前节点, [l,r]:修改的目标区间, val:要增加的值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">update</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r, <span class=\"type\">int</span> val)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> L = a[id].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> R = a[id].r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 情况1：当前节点区间完全被目标区间包含</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 直接修改当前节点，打上标记，不再向下</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l &lt;= L &amp;&amp; R &lt;= r) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[id].v += (<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)val * (R - L + <span class=\"number\">1</span>); <span class=\"comment\">// 更新当前节点的总和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[id].tag += val;                        <span class=\"comment\">// 打上标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 情况2：不完全包含，需要向下递归</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 【关键】：在分叉之前，必须先把身上的标记推下去！</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">push_down</span>(id);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = (L + R) &gt;&gt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l &lt;= mid) <span class=\"built_in\">update</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, l, r, val);      <span class=\"comment\">// 涉及左边就去左边</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (r &gt; mid)  <span class=\"built_in\">update</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, l, r, val);  <span class=\"comment\">// 涉及右边就去右边</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 回溯：更新父节点的值 (Push Up)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        a[id].v = a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v + a[id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>].v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//4，区间查询</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"title\">query</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> id, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//这个函数的功能是，从下标为id的结点出发，查询区间[l,r]的总和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> L = a[id].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> R = a[id].r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l &lt;= L &amp;&amp; R &lt;= r) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a[id].v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 【关键】：查询之前也要推标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">push_down</span>(id);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = (L + R) &gt;&gt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> res = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (l &lt;= mid) res += <span class=\"built_in\">query</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span>, l, r);<span class=\"comment\">//这个地方通过累加实现区间的分割</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (r &gt; mid)  res += <span class=\"built_in\">query</span>(id &lt;&lt; <span class=\"number\">1</span> | <span class=\"number\">1</span>, l, r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> res;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"动态开点\"><a href=\"#动态开点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"动态开点\"></a>动态开点</h1><h2 id=\"数据结构设计\"><a href=\"#数据结构设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据结构设计\"></a>数据结构设计</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//全局计数器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> cnt = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 代表当前用到了第几个节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> root;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">node</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> ls,rs;<span class=\"comment\">//左右子节点的下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> l,r;<span class=\"comment\">//包含的区间左右边检</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> val;<span class=\"comment\">//节点需要存储的属性，可以开多几个也没关系。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> tags;<span class=\"comment\">//标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">new_node</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//把生成新节点的部分独立出来，调用一次这个函数就cnt++，防止混淆</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ++cnt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[cnt].ls = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[cnt].rs = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[cnt].val = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[cnt].tag = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> cnt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"基础功能函数\"><a href=\"#基础功能函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础功能函数\"></a>基础功能函数</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">1</span>，更新父节点的值</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//从下标为p的节点出发遍历它所有的后代，以达到更新自己的目的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">push_up</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> p)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 注意：如果孩子不存在(是0)，那么那边的值就是0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// tree[0] 全局默认为0，所以直接加也没问题，但写清楚更好</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> left_val = (tree[p].ls ? tree[tree[p].ls].val : <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> right_val = (tree[p].rs ? tree[tree[p].rs].val : <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[p].val = left_val + right_val;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">2</span>,tags向下传递</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//对于tags的传递，普通线段树由于下标都是固定的比较方便，对于动态开点的线段树需要特殊的处理方法</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">push_down</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> p, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (tree[p].tag == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 没有标记，不用下传</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + (r - l) / <span class=\"number\">2</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> t = tree[p].tag;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// --- 左边 ---</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!tree[p].ls) tree[p].ls = <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>(); <span class=\"comment\">// 1. 没了就建</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> ls = tree[p].ls;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[ls].val += t * (mid - l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);        <span class=\"comment\">// 2. 更新数值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[ls].tag += t;                        <span class=\"comment\">// 3. 传递标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// --- 右边 ---</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!tree[p].rs) tree[p].rs = <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>(); <span class=\"comment\">// 1. 没了就建</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> rs = tree[p].rs;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[rs].val += t * (r - mid);            <span class=\"comment\">// 2. 更新数值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[rs].tag += t;                        <span class=\"comment\">// 3. 传递标记</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// --- 清空父节点 ---</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tree[p].tag = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">3</span>，区间修改</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//区间修改：将区间 [ql, qr] 内所有数都 + k</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">update</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;p, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r, <span class=\"type\">int</span> ql, <span class=\"type\">int</span> qr, <span class=\"type\">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 如果 p 还是 0（说明这里从来没被访问过），先建个号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!p) p = <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 1. 完全包含：直接改自己，打条子，走人</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ql &lt;= l &amp;&amp; r &lt;= qr) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        tree[p].val += (<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)k * (r - l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        tree[p].tag += k;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 2. 不完全包含：先下放标记，再分头行动</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">push_down</span>(p, l, r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + (r - l) / <span class=\"number\">2</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ql &lt;= mid) <span class=\"built_in\">update</span>(tree[p].ls, l, mid, ql, qr, k);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (qr &gt; mid)  <span class=\"built_in\">update</span>(tree[p].rs, mid + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, r, ql, qr, k);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 3. 孩子变了，重新算自己的总帐</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">push_up</span>(p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">4</span>，部分和查询</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//区间查询：查询[ql, qr]的和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"title\">query</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> p, <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, <span class=\"type\">int</span> r, <span class=\"type\">int</span> ql, <span class=\"type\">int</span> qr)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 如果节点不存在，或者区间没交集，那就是 0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!p) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 1. 完全包含：直接返回</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ql &lt;= l &amp;&amp; r &lt;= qr) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> tree[p].val;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 2. 要往下查，记得先推标记！否则孩子的数据是旧的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">push_down</span>(p, l, r); </span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> mid = l + (r - l) / <span class=\"number\">2</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> res = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ql &lt;= mid) res += <span class=\"built_in\">query</span>(tree[p].ls, l, mid, ql, qr);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (qr &gt; mid)  res += <span class=\"built_in\">query</span>(tree[p].rs, mid + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, r, ql, qr);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> res;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","feature":true,"text":"线段树初步建树函数1234567891011121314151617181920const int maxn = (int)1e5;struct node { ...","permalink":"/post/线段树及拓展","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.4k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"板子","slug":"板子","count":2,"path":"api/categories/板子.json"},{"name":"算法","slug":"板子/算法","count":2,"path":"api/categories/板子/算法.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"线段树","slug":"线段树","count":2,"path":"api/tags/线段树.json"},{"name":"DFS","slug":"DFS","count":3,"path":"api/tags/DFS.json"}],"to